'''Jonathan Vila''' (born [[March 06]] [[1986]] in [[O Porri<U+00F1>o]], [[Spain]]) is a [[Spain|Spanish]] [[soccer|football player]] who currently plays as a [[Midfielder]] for [[Celta de Vigo]] in the Spanish [[Segunda Divisi<U+00F3>n]].

